<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/19731>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Badister amazonus sp. n., dorsal aspect, female, ADP 051544; type locality. Head, including eyes, antennomeres 1 - 3, mouthparts, and anterior part of pronotum. Legend: a 3, antennomere 3; cl, clypeus; lb, labrum; lp 3, labial palpomere 3; mb, mandibular boss; mn, mandibular notch; mp 4, maxillary palpomere 4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/19731" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

